1146
01:18:24,360 --> 01:18:26,316
- Well, honey, you should do it. Hey!
- Hey, you guys!

1147
01:18:26,400 --> 01:18:28,311
- Merry Christmas.
- Hello.

1148
01:18:28,400 --> 01:18:31,358
June Fortier.

1149
01:18:33,800 --> 01:18:35,756
Get up here, you.

1150
01:18:35,840 --> 01:18:37,831
Clarice Mitchell.

1151
01:18:40,800 --> 01:18:43,234
- There she is.
- Oh, great!

1152
01:18:43,280 --> 01:18:45,191
- Hi, Kate. How are you?
- Hi, Ellen. How are you?

1153
01:18:45,280 --> 01:18:48,636
- Hi, Brian, George. Kate.
- Melissa Jamison.

1154
01:18:48,720 --> 01:18:50,631
Well, you just look wonderful.
You look wonderful.

1155
01:18:50,680 --> 01:18:52,716
- Well, thanks. Don't go get mushy on me.
- I just love the sweater.

1156
01:18:52,800 --> 01:18:55,872
- Oh, thanks.
- Evelyn Best.

1157
01:19:00,880 --> 01:19:03,440
Kate Gulden.

1158
01:19:24,080 --> 01:19:25,638
And Ellen Gulden.

1159
01:19:25,680 --> 01:19:27,989
We see you, Ellen.
You can't hide. Come on.

1160
01:19:28,080 --> 01:19:30,674
- We need all the Minnies up here.
- Come on, now.

1161
