to help her take her life?

1486
01:44:48,120 --> 01:44:52,716
If she did, Ellen, I can say with
some assurance no one in this office...

1487
01:44:52,800 --> 01:44:55,314
I did not help my mother
take her life.

1488
01:44:59,920 --> 01:45:01,751
Where was your father
on that last night?

1489
01:45:03,200 --> 01:45:06,078
He had a class.

1490
01:45:06,160 --> 01:45:08,958
He didn't come home
until she was already sleeping.

1491
01:45:15,840 --> 01:45:18,274
- George.
- Yeah.

1492
01:45:18,320 --> 01:45:20,754
- You came home so early.
- They cancelled my class.

1493
01:45:20,840 --> 01:45:25,038
Oh.

1494
01:45:30,680 --> 01:45:34,195
Hi, you pretty girl.

1495
01:45:34,280 --> 01:45:36,111
Did you miss me?

1496
01:45:36,200 --> 01:45:39,431
Oh, no.

1497
01:45:43,240 --> 01:45:47,119
I want to talk to George now.

1498
01:46:22,240 --> 01:46:25,232
