1499
01:46:25,320 --> 01:46:28,995
No one should have
to live like that.

1500
01:46:29,040 --> 01:46:30,917
No one.

1501
01:46:30,960 --> 01:46:33,520
Mom said that.

1502
01:46:37,640 --> 01:46:39,710
She was right.

1503
01:47:14,200 --> 01:47:16,077
Hey.

