1515
01:50:10,480 --> 01:50:12,311
I'm so sorry.

1516
01:50:17,320 --> 01:50:19,390
How are you?

1517
01:50:19,440 --> 01:50:23,319
Yeah. You okay?

1518
01:50:23,400 --> 01:50:26,233
