miss someone so much.

1519
01:50:26,320 --> 01:50:28,151
Oh, God.

1520
01:50:28,240 --> 01:50:30,834
I know.
I missed you too.

1521
01:50:36,480 --> 01:50:39,074
I know this isn't really
a good time to talk, but...

1522
01:50:39,120 --> 01:50:41,270
you know, when you're ready,
we should...

1523
01:50:41,360 --> 01:50:43,828
we should figure out what we're
going to do this year, you know.

1524
01:50:43,920 --> 01:50:47,117
- Don't you think?
- You know, Jordan, a lot has happened...

1525
01:50:47,160 --> 01:50:49,037
that you just don't understand.

1526
01:50:49,080 --> 01:50:52,436
And I'm sorry, but I don't think
you can understand.

1527
01:50:52,520 --> 01:50:54,351
What? What are you
talking about?

1528
01:50:54,440 --> 01:50:57,238
- Thank you for coming.
- EI?

