New job.

1540
01:52:47,840 --> 01:52:49,751
- You're writing again?
- Mm-hmm.

1541
01:52:49,840 --> 01:52:52,479
Feature writer for the Voice.

1542
01:52:52,560 --> 01:52:56,075
Hmph.
Congratulations.

1543
01:52:56,160 --> 01:52:57,991
Thanks.

1544
01:53:01,000 --> 01:53:02,831
I may want to speak to your father.

1545
01:53:06,480 --> 01:53:08,596
Anyway...

1546
01:53:08,680 --> 01:53:10,716
thank you.

1547
01:53:10,800 --> 01:53:12,631
Sure.

1548
01:53:18,800 --> 01:53:20,631
I'm sorry for your loss.

1549
01:53:20,720 --> 01:53:22,551
Thank you.

1550
01:54:03,640 --> 01:54:06,029
