of what she meant to me.

1578
01:56:32,000 --> 01:56:36,869
My... muse.

1579
01:56:36,920 --> 01:56:39,992
My... lovely wife.

1580
01:56:43,000 --> 01:56:45,230
My one true thing.

1581
01:56:48,920 --> 01:56:51,878
