1587
01:57:36,160 --> 01:57:37,991
Uh-huh.

1588
01:57:38,080 --> 01:57:42,232
And then four inches apart
so that the roots don't tangle...

1589
01:57:42,320 --> 01:57:44,880
and they'll just
look prettier.

1590
01:57:48,400 --> 01:57:50,675
